reviewText: I also am watching this on IFC! Weird, disturbing, campy and goofy. I love it!

I'm watching this on IFC on cable and the 'film' is best described as extremely odd. A low budget, surrealistic, absurd, silly movie and I'm only 15 minutes into it. The scene at the very beginning with the dancing girls in bikinis and the drummers and guys in weird 'naked suits' was out there. I'm tired and won't make it all the way through but can recommend it based on it's relentless strangeness and silliness ....
